3%BD/</guid><description>&lt;p>肾小球滤过是指血液流经肾小球毛细血管时，除蛋白质外，血浆中其余成分均能被滤过进入肾小囊腔内生成&lt;em>超滤液&lt;/em>，是尿生成的第一步。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>尿的生成与排出</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/</link><pubDate>Fri, 19 Nov 2021 16:18:02 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肾的功能解剖和肾血流量</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E8%82%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E5%92%8C%E8%82%BE%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F/</link><pubDate>Mon, 31 Jul 2023 13:20:51 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E8%82%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E5%92%8C%E8%82%BE%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肾小管和集合管的物质转运功能</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E8%82%BE%E5%B0%8F%E7%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E7%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E8%BD%AC%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</link><pubDate>Mon, 31 Jul 2023 20:36:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E8%82%BE%E5%B0%8F%E7%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E7%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E8%BD%AC%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</guid><description>&lt;p>正常人两肾生成的超滤液可达 180 L/d，而终尿量仅约 1.5 L/d，表明其中约 &lt;mark>99%&lt;/mark> 的水被肾小管和集合管重吸收。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>尿液的浓缩和稀释</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E5%B0%BF%E6%B6%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%93%E7%BC%A9%E5%92%8C%E7%A8%80%E9%87%8A/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 10:32:43 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E5%B0%BF%E6%B6%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%93%E7%BC%A9%E5%92%8C%E7%A8%80%E9%87%8A/</guid><description>&lt;p>尿液的渗透压可随着体内液体量的变化而大幅变动。当体内缺水时，尿液被浓缩，排出的尿渗透压明显高于血浆渗透压，即&lt;em>高渗尿&lt;/em>；当体内液体量过多时，尿液被稀释，排出尿液的渗透压低于血浆渗透压，为低渗尿。正常人尿液的渗透压在 50&amp;ndash;1200 m0sm/(kg·H&lt;sub>2&lt;/sub>0)之间波动，表明肾脏有较强的浓缩和稀释能力。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>根据机体缺水与否，正常成年人 24 小时尿量变动于 1.5&amp;ndash;2.5 L 之间。24 小时尿量超过 2.5L 称为多尿；24 小时尿量少于 400ml 称为少尿；如果 24 小时尿量不足 100ml，则称为无尿。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>尿生成的调节</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E5%B0%BF%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 11:53:31 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E5%B0%BF%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82/</guid><description>神经调节 肾交感神经在肾脏内不仅支配肾血管，还支配肾小管上皮细胞和球旁细胞，对肾小管的支配以近端小管、髓袢升支粗段和远端小管为主。肾交感神经兴</description></item><item><title>清除率</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E7%8E%87/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 13:37:18 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%B0%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA/%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E7%8E%87/</guid><description>&lt;p>两肾在单位时间（一般为每分钟）内能将一定毫升血浆中所含的某种物质（X）完全清除，这个能完全清除某物质的血浆毫升数就称为该物质的清除率（C）。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>泌尿系统疾病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%B3%8C%E5%B0%BF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 06 May 2023 16:36:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%B3%8C%E5%B0%BF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肾小球疾病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%B3%8C%E5%B0%BF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BE%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%83%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 May 2023 18:43:15 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%B3%8C%E5%B0%BF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BE%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%83%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>